<image 1> If the pH outside the cell decreases, would you expect the amount of amino acids transported into the cell to increase or decrease?

A. increase
B. decrease

If the pH outside the cell decreases, it would be expected to decrease the amount of amino acids transported into the cell, as the transport process is pH-dependent. Therefore, the correct answer is B. decrease.
